              Gentle devoted care

              We cherish and uplift every pets journey In Abu Dhabi

              At Furr, our team is devoted to the well-being of your beloved pets, offering gentle care and expert support at every stage of life, every day.

              Our mission is to provide a safe, nurturing space for pets and their families, with services ranging from routine check-ups to emergency care and dignified end-of-life support. Trust us to be there for you and your pet, always and compassionately, with kindness and expert care.

              Our values are rooted in empathy, honesty, and a drive for excellence, ensuring every experience at Furr is filled with warmth and respect. Since our founding in 2020, we have become a place where families find comfort and expert care for their cherished pets.
